Author: btzuko
Text: I try to keep my intake around 800, however I’ve been having days a lot lately where I compulsively eat one or two PB sandwiches on top of my 800 intake, which usually ends up around 1200 cals or maintenance. I just have to remind myself on those days that I will still lose on 1200 cals, and maintenance days aren’t the end of the world by any means.

Author: RenBumah
Text: That's one strange sounding meal but hey you enjoy it! Don't feel bad and fuck what the scale says
